      "author": "dvdsmpsn (David @ David Simpson Apps)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>I need an input field for an automation recipe  that’s similar to “Message” or “Email” in that it allows placeholders, like in the screenshot, but even better could be a single line, with my own help text at the top &amp; placeholder text in the input/textarea.</p>\n<p>Here’s the standard <strong>Message</strong> one:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/6/36acc015a4f46905af227dd9eb2b9d3fe4a0a932.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-12-05 at 12.08.49\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/6/36acc015a4f46905af227dd9eb2b9d3fe4a0a932_2_393x375.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-12-05 at 12.08.49\" width=\"393\" height=\"375\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-12-05 at 12.08.49</span><span class=\"informations\">932×888 40.4 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>I need a single line, like so:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/2/72d7543c540ead80a6c898328a78cffa0e3d023a.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2024-12-05 at 12.14.28\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/2/72d7543c540ead80a6c898328a78cffa0e3d023a_2_375x245.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-12-05 at 12.14.28\" width=\"375\" height=\"245\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2024-12-05 at 12.14.28</span><span class=\"informations\">944×618 38.9 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Ideally, you could customise:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The help text/label at the top</li>\n<li>The placeholder text</li>\n<li>Single or multi-line (input or textarea)</li>\n</ul>"
